                                        2871
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "Such deviation from the circular orbits is given by higher- order dynamics than Eqs. (12) and (13). In the second- order dynamics given by Eqs. (14) and (15), the multi- memory learning is qualitatively different from the zero- memory one. Indeed, Eqs. (14) and (15) obviously mean that interactions occur between the pair of "
                                },
